PrecisAmendment to the MUNICIPAL GRANTS REGULATIONS, 1980 which, for purposes of expediency, will enable the Minister to make payments of grants-in-lieu of taxes on lands that were transferred from the Department of Public Works to the Queens Quay West Land Corporation (formerly Harbourfront Corporation).
